{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"22aef85de3","title":"拟在铁边城以东地区消灭追敌","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"5e18db4b61","index":0,"year":1935,"month":10,"day":17,"articleId":"22aef85de3"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji7-2","name":"毛泽东全集第7卷(2)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji7-2.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji7-2":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"b90f196e05","type":"paragraph","text":"拟在铁边城以东地区消灭追敌”","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"22aef85de3"},{"id":"d80ba3a788","type":"paragraph","text":"（1935年10月17日）彭：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"22aef85de3"},{"id":"71b3d5f2a7","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）一纵队本日由木瓜城出发，进至离铁边城四十里之牛圈均坨一带宿营。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"22aef85de3"},{"id":"38742b0a46","type":"paragraph","text":"（二）毛炳文令陶时岳P进至环县、洪德城之线整理待命，其骑兵团仍令其尾追侦察。本日十四时，我后卫大队在木瓜城东端高山与敌接触，似即其骑兵团。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"22aef85de3"},{"id":"75f5850934","type":"paragraph","text":"（三）如该敌续追，拟于后日在铁边城以东地区回击消灭之","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"22aef85de3"},{"id":"0e078f94b6","type":"paragraph","text":"（四）为准备后日作战，一纵队明（十八）日拟进至铁边城以东之张家湾、杨家庙台之线宿营，后卫则在铁边城。后日以后卫部队引敌跟进，主力则从道侧突击之。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"22aef85de3"},{"id":"7f4c9596c5","type":"paragraph","text":"（五）二、三纵队明日务相当靠近一纵队宿营（史家河、阁家脸之线），以便后日协同消灭该敌","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"22aef85de3"},{"id":"5c46b4d492","type":"paragraph","text":"毛","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"22aef85de3"},{"id":"01a81e7b81","type":"paragraph","text":"十七日二十一时[1]这是毛泽东给红军陕甘支队司令员彭德怀的电报。12]毛炳文、陶时岳，当时分别任国民党军西北“”总司令部第一","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"22aef85de3"}],"page":{"id":"4262b66008","publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"22aef85de3","start":246,"end":246}}}},"__N_SSG":true}